20they%20may%20end%20up%20with%20none%20if%20inflation%20remains%20elevated%2C%20Bannister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20thinks%20the%20core%20PCE%20measure%20of%20inflation%20will%20stay%20closer%20to%20the%203%25%20level%2C%20forcing%20the%20central%20bank%20to%20keep%20rates%20where%20they%20are.%20That%20will%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20make%20bond%20market%20investors%20reassess%20yields%20on%20the%2010-year%20Treasury%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22982%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22core%20pce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67785f3a59d276c1cdb005b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221238%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStifel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20removed%20one-and-half%20cuts%2C%20I'd%20be%20pushing%20that%2010-year%20up%20closer%20to%205%25%2C%20from%204.6%25%20to%204.9%25%2C%20let's%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20every%20time%20we've%20gotten%20to%20the%20high%20fours%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20starts%20having%20a%20wobble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20ties%20into%20Bannister's%20worries%20about%20valuations.%20When%20valuations%20are%20elevated%2C%20future%20returns%20are%20muted.%20Yields%20on%20Treasurys%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20risk-free%2C%20so%20the%20extra%20compensation%20for%20taking%20on%20equity-market%20risk%20dwindles%2C%20making%20stocks%20look%20less%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20for%20instance%2C%2010-year%20yields%20went%20from%201.5%25%20to%204.9%25%20from%20January%20to%20October%20amid%20a%2025%25%20decline%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Bannister%20is%20skeptical%20that%20the%20US%20economy%20can%20continue%20to%20grow%20at%20its%20current%20pace%2C%20with%20GDP%20growth%20above%202%25.%20With%20wage%20growth%20coming%20down%20and%20inflation%20potentially%20remaining%20sticky%2C%20real%20wage%20growth%20could%20continue%20to%20shrink%2C%20hurting%20consumer%20spending%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStifel%20estimates%20GDP%20growth%20to%20fall%20to%20just%20over%201%25%20by%20December%202025.%20When%20GDP%20growth%20has%20slowed%2C%20stocks%20have%20usually%20slowed%20down%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222010%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gdp%20growth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677860719fc2c16009472c21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStifel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20doldrum%2C%20sort%20of%20like%20we%20had%20in%202011%20or%202015%2C%202016%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fed%20is%20deciding%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20that%20mid-cycle%20slowdown.%202015%20was%20very%20similar%20to%20what%202025%20looks%20like%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20Bannister's%20outlook%20is%20out%20of%20consensus.%20If%20the%20market's%20exuberance%20around%20AI%20continues%20and%20the%20economy%20stays%20on%20its%20soft-landing%20path%2C%20he%20could%20be%20wrong.%20Stocks%20vastly%20outperformed%20virtually%20all%20expectations%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20valuations%20as%20high%20as%20they%20are%2C%20there%20may%20be%20little%20room%20for%20error%20in%20the%20year%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-why-bullish-investors-wrong-stifel-bannister-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735985102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677863029fc2c16009472caf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-why-bullish-investors-wrong-stifel-bannister-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20valuations%20as%20high%20as%20they%20are%2C%20there%20may%20be%20little%20room%20for%20error%20in%20the%20year%20ahead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-why-bullish-investors-wrong-stifel-bannister-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20asked%207%20people%20how%20they%20knew%20they%20didn't%20want%20children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20with%20smiley%20face%20stickers%20on%20their%20face%20and%20baby%20cut%20out%20of%20image%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744ed3e9f2901eb6036c75f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20iStock%3B%20Natalie%20Ammari%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20becoming%20more%20common%20for%20people%20to%20choose%20to%20be%20child-free.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESeven%20people%20shared%20why%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20parents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20never%20desired%20kids%2C%20while%20others%20felt%20that%20bringing%20a%20child%20into%20this%20world%20would%20be%20unfair.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20societal%20expectation%20that%20people%20would%20grow%20up%2C%20get%20married%2C%20and%20have%202.5%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that's%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-free-boomer-not-having-kids-financial-freedom-sandwich-generation-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerns%20about%20overpopulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20environment%20to%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20remain%20independent%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-regret-not-having-kids-child-free-decision-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20want%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20seven%20people%20about%20why%20they're%20not%20interested%20in%20being%20parents%2C%20and%20their%20answers%20ranged%20from%20practical%20concerns%20about%20parenthood%20to%20just%20never%20feeling%20the%20desire%20to%20have%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EItzett%20Romero%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222068%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20poses%20with%20her%20hand%20on%20her%20chin%20in%20front%20of%20a%20brick%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6746027bede4eeae3929a7ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221551%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EItzett%20Romero.%3Cp%3EItzett%20Romero%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2037%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJob%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Digital%20marketer%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40itzettromero%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20creator%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20she%20knew%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20kids%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Romero%20told%20BI%20she%20knew%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20as%20she%20spent%20much%20of%20her%20adolescence%20helping%20to%20care%20for%20her%20younger%20siblings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20she%20doesn't%20want%20them%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Romero%20is%20the%20oldest%20of%20three%20children%2C%20and%20because%20of%20the%20large%20age%20gap%20with%20her%20siblings%2C%20she%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-an-only-child-but-only-one-expected-have-kids-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildcare%20growing%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20understood%20the%20sacrifices%20people%20make%20when%20they%20have%20children%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20something%20she%20wanted%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20very%20much%20understanding%20not%20just%20the%20Disney%20version%20or%20what%20the%20media%20portrays%20as%20having%20kids%2C%20but%20the%20more%20rea