oundation%20has%20backed%20efforts%20like%20developing%20and%20delivering%20vaccines%20to%20poverty-stricken%20countries%2C%20supporting%20agriculture%20and%20reducing%20food%20insecurity%20in%20developing%20nations%2C%20and%20committed%20more%20than%20%242%20billion%20to%20fight%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20foundation%20has%20also%20received%20criticism%20from%20global%20health%20and%20development%20experts%2C%20who%20have%20accused%20the%20organization%20of%20lacking%20transparency%20and%20accountability.%20Despite%20being%20a%20private%2C%20unelected%20entity%2C%20the%20foundation%20has%20had%20major%20effects%20and%20implications%20on%20public%20policy%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20its%20critics%20say%20it%20makes%20decisions%20based%20on%20the%20whims%20of%20its%20billionaire%20trustees%20rather%20than%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%20has%20poured%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20into%20agricultural%20development%20in%20Africa%20over%20the%20years%20via%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20revolution%26quot%3B%20emphasizing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-farms-super-crops-investment-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnological%20innovations%20in%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20multiple%20organizations%20have%20called%20the%20efforts%20a%20failure%20and%20urged%20the%20foundation%20to%20instead%20listen%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20African%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmelinda-french-gates-how-it-feels-to-be-a-billionaire-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelinda%20Gates%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20acknowledged%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20foundation's%20strategies.%20For%20instance%2C%20despite%20spending%20billions%20on%20improving%20the%20US%20education%20system%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20boosting%20high%20school%20graduation