%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20women%20belong%20to%20their%20(Congress%20and%20BJP)%20party.%20They%20have%20not%20come%20from%20Punjab%2C%20the%20women%20in%20Punjab%20are%20with%20us.%20They%20have%20faith%20in%20AAP.%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20should%20officially%20announce%20that%20they%20are%20contesting%20elections%20together%20against%20AAP%20in%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20former%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20take%20Congress%20seriously.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20that%20AAP's%20governance%20model%20has%20consistently%20delivered%20on%20promises%2C%20citing%20free%20water%20supply%20to%20over%2012%20lakh%20families%20in%20Delhi%20as%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20However%2C%20he%20alleged%20that%20issues%20arose%20in%20his%20absence%2C%20resulting%20in%20exorbitant%20water%20bills%20for%20many%20residents.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20publicly%20and%20officially%20announce%20that%20those%20who%20think%20their%20bills%20are%20wrong%2C%20they%20need%20not%20pay.%20Wait%20for%20the%20elections%3B%20AAP%20will%20form%20the%20government%2C%20and%20we%20will%20waive%20off%20those%20wrong%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20from%20Punjab%20accused%20the%20AAP-led%20Punjab%20government%20of%20not%20fulfilling%20its%20pre-election%20promise%20to%20provide%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20every%20woman%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20protesters%20allege%20that%20AAP%20has%20prepared%20similar%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20women%20in%20Delhi%20ahead%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20scheduled%20this%20year.%20AAP's%20Mukhya%20Mantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20in%20Delhi%20proposes%20a%20Rs%202%2C100%20monthly%20stipend%20for%20women%20over%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20which%20has%20struggled%20to%20regain%20political%20ground%20in%20Delhi%2C%20capitalised%20on%20the%20protests