Department%20of%20Defense%20classifies%20it%20as%20a%20cruiser.%20Many%20observers%20compare%20it%20to%20the%20US%20Navy's%20own%20cruisers%2C%20which%20have%20performed%20a%20similar%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20your%20criteria%2C%20the%20Type%20055%20is%20the%20best%20or%20second-best%20surface%20combatant%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Carlson%2C%20a%20retired%20US%20Navy%20captain%20and%20naval%20analyst%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20US%20Navy%20seeks%20to%20divest%20from%20its%20aging%20cruiser%20fleet%2C%20China%20is%20expanding%20its%20fleet%20at%20a%20breakneck%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228dfd6baf-e1fc-4693-9cab-0881aaff0696%5C%22%3EType%20055%20'Renhai'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20commissioning%20of%20the%20first-in-class%20Nanchang%20in%202020%20revealed%20China%20had%20launched%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20surface%20combatants.%20China%20may%20build%20up%20to%2016%20of%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676ed34f9de00e389eb39171%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20commissioning%20of%20the%20first-in-class%20Nanchang%20in%202020%20revealed%20China%20had%20launched%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20surface%20combatants.%20China%20may%20build%20up%20to%2016%20of%20them.%3Cp%3EFu%20Tian%2FChina%20News%20Service%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20desire%20for%20a%20massive%20surface%20combatant%20dates%20back%20to%20the%201960s.%20China%20initiated%20an%20%26quot%3B055%26quot%3B%20program%20in%20the%20mid-1970s%2C%20then%20canceled%20it%20in%201983%20due%20to%20weaknesses%20in%20its%20industrial%20base%20and%20technological%20know-how.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20decades%20later%2C%20however%2C%20China's%20booming%20economy%20enabled%20its%20shipbuilding%20industry%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fthreat-chinas-shipbuilding-empire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20emphasized%20modernizing%20the%20navy%20and%20building%20or%20acquiring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-china-navy-plan-replenishment-ships-modernization-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efleet%20oilers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimproved-chinese-nuclear-submarines-could-counter-us-navy-dominance-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enuclear%20submarines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20guided%20missile%20warships%2C%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20keel%20of%20the%20first%20Type%20055%2C%20Nanchang%2C%20was%20laid%20in%20December%202014%2C%20just%20three%20months%20before%20the%20keel%20of%20China's%20first%20domestically%20built%20carrier%2C%20Shandong%2C%20was%20laid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nanchang%20was%20commissioned%20in%202020%2C%20it%20made%20the%20class%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with.%20Measuring%20590%20feet%20long%20and%20displacing%2012%2C000-13%2C000%20tons%2C%20it%20is%20the%20largest%20class%20of%20surface%20combatant%20China%20has%20ever%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20Type%20055%2C%20which%20NATO%20classifies%20as%20the%20Renhai-class%2C%20is%20fitted%20with%20112%20vertical%20launch%20system%20(VLS)%20cells%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20launch%20missiles.%20Sixty-four%20cells%20are%20positioned%20forward%20of%20the%20bridge%20in%20an%208x8%20configuration%20and%2048%20are%20located%20aft%20in%20a%206x8%20configuration.%20These%20VLS%20cells%20have%20both%20cold%20and%20hot%20launch%20capability%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20field%20a%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcimsec.org%2Ffighting-dmo-pt-8-chinas-anti-ship-firepower-and-mass-firing-schemes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediverse%20missile%20arsenal%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20in%20a%20cold%20launch%2C%20a%20missile%20is%20ejected%20from%20the%20cell%20via%20pressurized%20gas%20before%20its%20engine%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20arsenal%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissilethreat.csis.org%2Fmissile%2Fyj-18%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYJ-18%3C%2Fa%3E%20anti-ship%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20CJ-10%20land-attack%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20and%20HHQ-9%20surface-to-air%20missiles%20(SAMs)%2C%20which%20have%20ranges%20of%20around%20335%20miles%2C%20497%20miles%2C%20and%20124%20miles%2C%20respectively.%20The%20class%20may%20also%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20Yu-8%20anti-submarine%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20China%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hisutton.com%2FChinese-Hypersonic-Missile-YJ-21.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etested%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20cold%20launch%20of%20a%20YJ-21%20hypersonic%20missile%20from%20a%20Type%20055's%20VLS%20cells.%20The%20missile%20reportedly%20has%20an%20approximate%20range%20of%20932%20miles%2C%20a%20cruising%20speed%20of%20Mach%206%2C%20and%20a%20terminal%20speed%20of%20Mach%2010%2C%C2%A0which%20makes%20it%20challenging%20to%20intercept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Type%20055%20also%20features%20a%20single%20box%20launcher%20with%2025%20HHQ-10%20short-range%20SAMs%2C%20four%20Type%20726%20defensive%20launchers%20capable%20of%20launching%20chaff%2C%20flares%2C%20and%20decoys%2C%202%20triple-tubed%20torpedo%20launchers%20with%20Yu-7%20torpedoes%2C%20a%20single%2011-barelled%20H%2FPJ-11%20Close-in%20weapon%20system%20(CIWS)%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FD__Mitch%2Fstatus%2F1137803229692141568%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH%2FPJ-38%3C%2Fa%3E%20130%20mm%20naval%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20stern%2C%20a%20helicopter%20deck%20and%20hangar%20can%20house%20two%20helicopters%20capable%20of%20tracking%20submarines%20and%20helping%20with%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Type%20055%20is%20also%20brimming%20with%20modern%20radars%2C%20sensors%2C%20and%20other%20electronics.%20This%20includes%20four%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usni.org%2Fmagazines%2Fproceedings%2F2021%2Fjune%2Fair-defense-destroyers-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EType%20346B%20Dragon%20Eye%3C%2Fa%3E%20S-band%20active%20electronically%20scanned%20array%20(AESA)%20radars%20mounted%20on%20the%20superstructure%20and%20four%20X-band%20radars%20housed%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcimsec.org%2F22119-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintegrated%20mast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20the%20first%20Chinese%20warship%20with%20dual-band%20planar%20radar%20arrays.%20Its%20hull-mounted%20sonar%20can%20be%20enhanced%20by%20towed%20active%20array%20sonars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20arsenal%20and%20sensor%2Felectronic%20suite%2C%20the%20Type%20055%20can%20take%20on%20an%20anti-ship%2C%20anti-submarine%2C%20anti-air%2C%20or%20land-attack%20role%2C%20making%20it%20the%20best%20candidate%20for%20a%20carrier%20escort.%20It's%20also%20capable%20of%20operating%20as%20a%20command%20flagship%20for%20any%20PLAN%20surface%20action%20group%20without%20a%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20has%20speculated%20that%20China%20wants%20to%20incorporate%20ballistic%20missile%20defense%20(BMD)%20systems%20on%20the%20Type%20055%2C%20which%20could%20enable%20it%20to%20serve%20in%20a%20BMD%2Fanti-satellite%20role%20similar%20to%20Japan's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-building-warships-to-counter-north-korean-missile-threat-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBMD%20destroyers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEight%20Type%20055s%20are%20in%20service.%20At%20least%20three%20more%20are%20reportedly%20in%20varying%20stages%20of%20construction.%20China%20may%20build%20as%20many%20as%2016%20Type%20055s%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20young%20age%2C%20the%20class%20has%20already%20gained%20a%20reputation%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20surface%20combatants%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20the%20Type%20055%20is%20the%20most%20capable%20in%20anti-surface%20warfare%2C%20but%20not%20as%20capable%20in%20the%20air%20defense%20and%20BMD%20role%20as%20a%20US%20%5BArleigh%5D%20Burke%20DDG%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlson%2C%20the%20retired%20US%20Navy%20captain%2C%20said.%20He%20said%20the%20Type%20055's%20strike%20and%20ASW%20capabilities%20are%20about%20the%20same%20as%20its%20American%20counterpart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6631e36-fde6-4fd9-80f8-2399250ce913%5C%22%3ETiconderoga-class%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cruisers%20like%20the%20USS%20Normandy%20play%20key%20roles%20in%20carrier%20strike%20groups.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676ed225bec2d3fdefeb2ed3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECruisers%20like%20the%20USS%20Normandy%20play%20key%20roles%20in%20carrier%20strike%20groups.%3Cp%3EMC2%20Malachi%20Lakey%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20size%2C%20armament%2C%20and%20mission%20of%20the%20Type%20055%20are%20often%20compared%20to%20the%20US%20Navy's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-ticonderoga-class-guided-missile-cruisers-failed-modernization-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiconderoga-class%20cruiser%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Measuring%20567%20feet%20long%2C%20displacing%20around%2010%2C000%20tons%2C%20and%20first%20entering%20service%20in%201983%2C%20the%20ships%20of%20the%20class%20are%20considerably%20older%20and%20smaller%20than%20the%20Type%20055s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Ticonderogas%20are%20no%20less%20potent%20and%20have%20a%20larger%20missile%20arsenal%2C%20with%20two%20sets%20of%2061%20Mk%2041%20VLS%20cells%20able%20to%20carry%20122%20missiles%20and%20two%20quad-tubed%20Mk-141%20launchers%20at%20the%20stern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Mark%2045%205-inch%20guns%20are%20present%20at%20the%20stem%20and%20stern%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20Phalanx%20CIWS'%20and%20two%20triple-tubed%20Mark%2032%20torpedo%20tubes%20capable%20of%20firing%20Mk%2046%20or%20Mk%2050%20torpedoes.%20A%20helicopter%20hangar%20capable%20of%20housing%20two%20MH-60R%20Seahawk%20helicopters%20provides%20additional%20ASW%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20makeup%20of%20each%20Ticonderoga's%20missile%20arsenal%20is%20dependent%20on%20its%20mission%2C%20as%20it%20is%20capable%20of%20carrying%20a%20host%20of%20different%20missiles.%20These%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissilethreat.csis.org%2Fmissile%2Ftomahawk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETomahawk%3C%2Fa%3E%20cruise%20missiles%20for%20ground%20targets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissilethreat.csis.org%2Fmissile%2Fharpoon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarpoon%3C%2Fa%3E%20anti-ship%20missiles%20for%20hostile%20ships%2C%20and%20RUM-139%20VL-ASROC%20anti-submarine%20missiles%20for%20enemy%20subs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20missiles%20have%20ranges%20of%20up%20to%201%2C500%20miles%2C%20149%20miles%2C%20and%2010%20miles%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ticonderoga's%20main%20role%2C%20however%2C%20is%20air%20defense.%20It%20can%20carry%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20anti-air%20missiles%2C%20including%20Evolved%20Sea%20Sparrow%20SAMs%2C%20and%20all%20active%20variants%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navy.mil%2FResources%2FFact-Files%2FDisplay-FactFiles%2FArticle%2F2169011%2Fstandard-missile%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStandard%20Missile%3C%2Fa%3E%20family%3B%20the%20SM-2%20Blocks%20III%2C%20IIIA%2C%20IIIB%2C%20and%20IV%3B%20the%20SM-3%2C%20and%20the%20SM-6.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20missiles%2C%20which%20can%20intercept%20targets%20ranging%20from%2035%20miles%20to%20over%20200%2C%20enable%20the%20Ticonderoga%20to%20provide%20an%20effective%20air%20defense%20umbrella%20against%20low-%20and%20high-altitude%20threats%2C%20including%20helicopters%2C%20drones%2C%20jets%2C%20and%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20an%20SM-3%20fired%20from%20the%20cruiser%20USS%20Lake%20Erie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thespacereview.com%2Farticle%2F4198%2F1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edestroyed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20defunct%20satellite%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20some%20150%20miles%2C%20demonstrating%20its%20ability%20to%20perform%20anti-satellite%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20defining%20asset%20of%20the%20Ticonderogas%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissilethreat.csis.org%2Fdefsys%2Fan-spy-1-radar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAN%2FSPY-1%3C%2Fa%3E%20passive%20phased%20array%20radar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20vital%20component%20of%20the%20AEGIS%20Combat%20System%2C%20an%20advanced%20and%20integrated%20naval%20defense%20system%20that%20combines%20command%2C%20detecting%2C%20tracking%2C%20and%20weapons%20control%20for%20comprehensive%20management%20of%20air%2C%20surface%2C%20and%20submarine%20threats%2C%20and%20which%20the%20Ticonderogas%20were%20the%20first%20ships%20to%20employ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-seven%20Ticonderoga-class%20cruisers%20were%20built%20between%201980%20and%201994%2C%20but%20only%20nine%20are%20in%20active%20service%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b31b5c2d-f93b-4f83-b09e-21f0796cbde5%5C%22%3ECruiser%20gap%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20US%20Navy%20is%20moving%20to%20retire%20most%20of%20its%20nine%20cruisers%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676ed541bec2d3fdefeb2f21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20is%20moving%20to%20retire%20most%20of%20its%20nine%20cruisers%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3Cp%3EMC2%20Indra%20Beaufort%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20importance%20of%20the%20Ticonderoga%20and%20the%20Type%20055%20to%20their%20respective%20fleets%20is%20hard%20to%20overstate.%20Their%20displacement%2C%20arsenal%20size%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20perform%20multiple%20missions%20and%20operate%20as%20flagships%20puts%20them%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20of%20most%20important%20surface%20combatants%20%E2%80%94%20second%2C%20perhaps%2C%20only%20to%20the%20carriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20acknowledgment%20of%20their%20capability%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20officially%20designates%20the%20Type%20055%20as%20a%20cruiser%2C%20despite%20China's%20own%20designation%20of%20destroyer%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20a%20PR%20move%20intended%20to%20make%20the%20PLAN%20seem%20less%20aggressive.%20(Destroyers%20typically%20have%20smaller%20displacements%20and%20arsenals%20than%20cruisers%20and%20play%20a%20less%20prominent%20role%20in%20the%20fleet.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20their%20deployments%20are%20carefully%20monitored%2C%20with%20their%20standalone%20voyages%20seen%20as%20intentional%20shows%20of%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EType%20055s%20have%20sailed%20in%20the%20waters%20off%20Alaska%20in%202021%2C%202022%2C%20and%202024%2C%20including%20as%20part%20of%20joint%20Chinese-Russian%20patrols.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERecently%2C%20a%20Type%20055%20visited%20the%20island%20nation%20of%20Vanuatu%2C%20signaling%20to%20some%20that%20China%20was%20trying%20to%20increase%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ticonderogas%20have%20also%20been%20on%20the%20move.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20cruiser%20USS%20Port%20Royal%20sailed%20through%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20in%20a%20sign%20to%20China.%20More%20recently%2C%20in%20June%2C%20USS%20Normandy%20participated%20in%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20off%20Norway%2C%20and%20in%20September%2C%20USS%20Bunker%20Hill%20took%20part%20in%20a%20massive%20five-nation%20drill%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20both%20navies%20currently%20have%20nine%20cruisers%20in%20active%20service%2C%20this%20will%20not%20be%20the%20case%20for%20long.%20While%20China%20has%20only%20just%20entered%20the%20cruiser%20game%2C%20the%20US%20Navy%20has%20been%20seeking%20to%20decommission%20its%20cruisers%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20argues%20that%20the%20cruisers%20have%20approached%2C%20passed%2C%20or%20will%20soon%20pass%20their%20expected%20service%20lives%20and%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20keeping%20the%20ships%20up%20and%20running%20is%20draining%20the%20service%20of%20funds%20and%20shipyard%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20USS%20Vella%20Gulf%20lasted%20just%20one%20week%20into%20a%20deployment%20before%20leaks%20in%20a%20fuel%20tank%20required%20it%20to%20return%20to%20port.%20More%20mechanical%20problems%20were%20soon%20uncovered%2C%20and%20the%20ship%20spent%20two%20months%20undergoing%20repairs%20before%20it%20could%20rejoin%20its%20carrier%20strike%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavy%20Secretary%20Carlos%20Del%20Toro%20has%20even%20testified%20to%20Congress%20that%20some%20of%20the%20ships%20were%20unsafe.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-ticonderoga-class-guided-missile-cruisers-failed-modernization-2024-12%23a-temporary-fix-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodernization%20effort%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20seven%20cruisers%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20went%20as%20much%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-faces-another-fight-to-get-rid-of-its-cruisers-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E200%25%20over%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fell%20years%20behind%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20wants%20to%20divest%20from%20ships%20it%20says%20it%20doesn't%20need%20and%20invest%20in%20new%20vessels%20that%20it%20argues%20can%20adequately%20fill%20in%20for%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Ticonderogas%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20like%20the%20new%20Flight%20III%20variant%20of%20the%20Arleigh%20Burke-class%20destroyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Congress%20has%20so%20far%20rejected%20the%20Navy's%20plans%20to%20retire%20all%20of%20its%20remaining%20cruisers%20due%20to%20fears%20that%20they%20play%20too%20important%20a%20role%20in%20countering%20China%2C%20whose%20increasing%20might%20could%20be%20a%20means%20to%20try%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-invasion-taiwan-seizing-ports-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseize%20the%20island%20of%20Taiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Ticonderogas%20%E2%80%94%20Vicksburg%2C%20Cowpens%2C%20Leyte%20Gulf%2C%20and%20Antietam%20%E2%80%94%20were%20decommissioned%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20On%20November%204%2C%20Del%20Toro%20announced%20that%20the%20Navy%20would%20operate%20three%20cruisers%20planned%20to%20be%20decommissioned%20in%202026%20into%202029%2C%20effectively%20extending%20their%20service%20lives.%20The%20rest%20are%20planned%20to%20be%20decommissioned%20before%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20will%20continue%20building%20Type%20055s%20at%20rates%20virtually%20unthinkable%20to%20US%20shipyards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBenjamin%20Brimelow%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20covering%20international%20military%20and%20defense%20issues.%20He%20holds%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20Global%20Affairs%20with%20a%20concentration%20in%20international%20security%20from%20the%20Fletcher%20School%20of%20Law%20and%20Diplomacy.%20His%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Business%20Insider%20and%20the%20Modern%20War%20Institute%20at%20West%20Point.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-chinese-navy-ticonderoga-class-type-055-destroyer-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735981262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676f12b5bec2d3fdefeb4f21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-chinese-navy-ticonderoga-class-type-055-destroyer-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20new%20Type%20055%20destroyer%20rivals%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20US's%20aging%20Ticonderoga%20class%20and%20may%20exceed%20it%20in%20threatening%20other%20ships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Benjamin%20Brimelow)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-chinese-navy-ticonderoga-class-type-055-destroyer-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rolexes%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20financial%20security%3A%20What%20bitcoin's%20latest%20rally%20has%20bought%20for%20some%20patient%20retail%20bulls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20of%20a%20hand%20holding%20a%20shiny%20bitcoin%2C%20surrounded%20by%20falling%20money%2C%20upward%20trending%20arrow%2C%20and%20grid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6762077d6c531c315b88dea6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbtc-usd%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E's%20116%25%20climb%20in%202024%20made%20fortunes%20for%20many%20individual%20investors.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERetail%20investors%20say%20they've%20used%20the%20money%20for%20cars%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20financial%20freedom.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEven%20as%20the%20crypto%20sees%20big%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20many%20say%20they'll%20hold%20onto%20some%20bitcoin%20forever.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20stunning%202024%20rally%20minted%20fortunes%20for%20many%20everyday%20traders%2C%20some%20of%20whom%2C%20after%20years%20of%20facing%20off%20with%20skeptics%2C%20say%20they've%20used%20the%20cryptocurrency%20to%20buy%20Rolexes%2C%20pay%20for%20homes%2C%20engagement%20rings%2C%20and%20peace%20of%20mind.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20investors%20who%20got%20in%20on%20bitcoin%20before%20the%20hype%20%E2%80%94%20and%20won%20big%20amid%20the%20crypto's%20dizzying%20116%25%20rally%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%2C%20whose%20gains%20were%20verified%20through%20brokerage%20and%20account%20statements%20reviewed%20by%20BI%2C%20extolled%20the%20investment%20as%20life-changing%E2%80%94and%20emphasized%20that%20they%20plan%20to%20keep%20holding%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20crypto%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaun%2C%20a%20retail%20trader%20who%20first%20bought%20bitcoin%20in%202013%2C%20estimates%20he's%20made%20over%20%24300%2C000%20from%20the%20crypto%20on%20a%20total%20investment%20of%20%2425%2C000%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20got%20into%20bitcoin%20when%20he%20funded%20a%20wallet%20to%20play%20online%20poker.%20When%20he%20stopped%20playing%2C%20he%20had%20around%20%24100%20worth%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20which%20he%20forgot%20about%20until%20he%20stumbled%20across%20a%20news%20article%20about%20the%20token%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%20to%20buy%20more%20bitcoin%2C%20funneling%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20every%20time%20its%20price%20dipped.%20By%202017%2C%20the%20year%20bitcoin%20rocketed%201%2C338%25%2C%20he%20realized%20he%20had%20struck%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%20seeing%20myself%20retiring%20as%20this%20multimillionaire.%20Like%2C%20oh%20my%20god%2C%20I%20don't%20even%20care%20about%20my%20job%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20somewhere%20in%20the%20mid-twenties%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20oh%20my%20God%2C%20this%20is%20amazing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20cashed%20out%20around%20%2425%2C000%20to%20purchase%20a%20Rolex%2C%20his%20first%20big-ticket%20purchase.%20Several%20years%20later%2C%20he%20cashed%20out%20another%20%2430%2C000%20to%20purchase%20an%20engagement%20ring%20for%20his%20wife%20and%20more%20to%20help%20fund%20his%20wedding%2C%20which%20he%20said%20cost%20around%20%2480%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Shaun%2C%20the%20gains%20were%20staggering.%20Growing%20up%2C%20his%20family%20was%20lower-income%2C%20and%20he%20knew%20nothing%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvesting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20always%20jokes%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20like%20luxury%20things%20now%20%E2%80%A6%20it's%20because%20we%20grew%20up%20so%20poor.%20I%20now%20value%20the%20finer%20things%20in%20life%2C%20things%20I%20never%20would've.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20as%20bitcoin%20was%20sprinting%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-today-hits-100k-donald-trump-crypto-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shaun%20sold%20another%20%24200%2C000%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20million-dollar%20investment%20property%20with%20his%20wife.%20He%20still%20holds%20around%20%24100%2C000%20worth%20of%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20goes%20to%20zero%2C%20at%20least%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20it%20to%20buy%20something%20that%20will%20literally%20provide%20income%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20investors%20told%20BI%20that%20bitcoin%20has%20helped%20them%20feel%20more%20financially%20secure%2C%20particularly%20for%20retirement%20or%20for%20taking%20care%20of%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20bitcoin%20trader%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20for%20privacy%20reasons%2C%20said%20he%20made%20around%20%24100%2C000%20investing%20in%20bitcoin%2C%20which%20allowed%20him%20to%20pay%20off%20his%20car.%20Though%20he%20got%20into%20bitcoin%20relatively%20late%E2%80%94%20in%202022%E2%80%94his%20%2416%2C000%20investment%20ballooned%20to%20more%20than%20%24120%2C000%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20statements%20viewed%20by%20BI%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20hear%20my%20mom%20saying%20that%20investments%20were%20meant%20to%20be%20sold%20when%20you%20need%20the%20money.%20So%2C%20I%20took%20some%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20investment%20remains%20untouched.%20Still%2C%20it%20gave%20him%20enough%20financial%20security%20to%20travel%20and%20spend%20three%20years%20taking%20care%20of%20a%20sick%20family%20member%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20so%20a%20life%20insurance%20policy%20for%20me%2C%20where%20if%20I%20passed%20away%2C%20I%20can%20give%20it%20off%20to%20my%20immediate%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20trader%20who%20requested%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20but%20shared%20his%20account%20statements%20with%20BI%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20retire%20early%20after%20he%20began%20investing%20in%20bitcoin%20in%202011.%20His%20total%20holdings%20were%20worth%20around%20%2413.8%20million%20when%20he%20spoke%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20recently%20able%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20retire%20early.%20He%20now%20spends%20most%20of%20his%20time%20with%20his%20family%20and%20working%20on%20his%20hobbies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRefreshing%20and%20stress-free%2C%20knowing%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20deal%20with%20other%20people%20%5Band%5D%20work%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20how%20his%20quality%20of%20life%20since%20his%20windfall.%20%26quot%3BSecure%20knowing%20my%20family%20is%20financially%20covered%20and%20if%20anything%20happens%20to%20me%2C%20my%20wife%20doesn't%20need%20to%20worry.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20retail%20trader%20named%20Keaton%20has%20made%20around%20%24100%2C000%20on%20bitcoin%20since%20he%20first%20invested%20in%20the%20crypto%20after%20graduating%20from%20high%20school%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%202010s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20a%20small%20investment%20after%20a%20friend%20told%20him%20about%20bitcoin%2C%20and%20began%20putting%20in%20more%20money%20after%20tuning%20in%20to%20talks%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrostrategy-bitcoin-100000-michael-saylor-crypto-markets-investing-strategy-analysis-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20Saylor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20business%20software%20firm%20Microstrategy%20and%20a%20highly%20vocal%20bitcoin%20evangelist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20began%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates%20this%20year%2C%20Keaton%20took%20out%20around%20%2435%2C000%20in%20debt%20and%20put%20it%20into%20bitcoin.%20When%20he%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20his%20holdings%20were%20worth%20nearly%20%24130%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20hasn't%20drastically%20changed%20his%20day-to-day%20life%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20the%20nest%20egg%20has%20given%20him%20confidence%20that%20he%20can%20put%20down%20a%20down%20payment%20for%20a%20home%20and%20support%20his%20family%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20life-changing%20money%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20I%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20things%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3B%20I'm%20in%20a%20position%20where%20I%20could%20put%20a%20substantial%20amount%20down%20for%20a%20house.%20I%20can%20pay%20off%20my%20car%20loan%20if%20I%20wanted.%20I%20can%20be%20completely%20debt-free.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin%20has%20stumbled%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20dropping%20around%208%25%20from%20its%20all-time%20high%20above%20%24108%2C000%20reached%20in%20mid-December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20of%20the%20bulls%20say%20selling%20is%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%20staying%20loyal%20to%20the%20mindset%20of%20HODL%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deliberate%20misspelling%20of%20%26quot%3Bhold%26quot%3B%20that's%20as%20also%20an%20acronym%20in%20crypto%20circles%20for%20%26quot%3Bhold%20on%20for%20dear%20life.%2