20R%20Chidambaram%20died%20this%20morning%20in%20Mumbai%20at%20the%20age%20of%2088.%20He%20was%20a%20key%20player%20in%20both%20of%20India's%20atomic%20explosions%20at%20Pokhran%20in%201974%20and%201998.%20He%20served%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20India's%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%20and%20later%20became%20the%20Principal%20Scientific%20Adviser%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20He%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20for%20his%20stellar%20contributions%20to%20making%20India%20a%20nuclear%20weapons%20state.%20A%20nuclear%20physicist%20by%20training%2C%20he%20was%20known%20for%20his%20brevity%2C%20genteel%20manner%2C%20and%20discretion%20in%20safeguarding%20national%20secrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20headed%20the%20nuclear%20component%20of%20the%201998%20Operation%20Shakti%20at%20Pokhran%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20rare%20atomic%20scientists%20who%20contributed%20to%20both%20Smiling%20Buddha%20in%201974%20and%20Operation%20Shakti%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20passing%2C%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20Dr%20Ajit%20Kumar%20Mohanty%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BDr%20Chidambaram%20was%20a%20doyen%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20whose%20contributions%20furthered%20India's%20nuclear%20prowess%20and%20strategic%20self-reliance.%20His%20loss%20is%20an%20irreparable%20one%20for%20the%20scientific%20community%20and%20the%20nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fpokhran-2-nuclear-weapons-testing_650x400_81526020399.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201974%2C%20when%20India%20secretly%20transported%20the%20plutonium%20used%20in%20the%20atomic%20blasts%2C%20Dr%20Chidambaram%20reportedly%20sat%20on%20the%20protected%20chest%20carrying%20the%20'plutonium%20ball'%20as%20it%20was%20transported%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Pokhran.%20He%20is%20also%20believed%20to%20have%20coined%20the%20term%20'peaceful%20nuclear%20explosion'%20for%20the%201974%20Pokhran%20test.%20For%20his%20role%20in%20the%20atomic%20blasts%2C%20he%20was%20denied%20a%20visa%20to%20enter%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20as%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20was%20under%20sanctions%20at%20that%20time.%20In%201998%2C%20as%20head%20of%20the%20atomic%20establishment%2C%20he%20oversaw%20five%20atomic%20explosions%20that%20declared%20India%20a%20nuclear%20weapons%20state.%20That%20year%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20at%20the%20Pokhran%20range%20standing%20alongside%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20firm%20believer%20in%20self-reliance-later%20called%20Atmanirbharta%20-%20Dr%20Chidambaram%20strongly%20opposed%20reliance%20on%20imported%20technology.%20He%20once%20told%20NDTV's%20Pallava%20Bagla%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20one%20imports%20technology%2C%20one%20only%20gets%20obsolete%20technology%2C%20as%20no%20country%20seeks%20to%20share%20cutting-edge%2C%20state-of-the-art%20technical%20breakthroughs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ER.%20Chidambaram%2C%20who%20has%20just%20passed%20away%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20titans%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20in%20India%20for%20well%20over%20five%20decades.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20had%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20Pokhran-1%20in%20May%201974%20and%20was%20central%20to%20Pokhran-2%20in%20May%201998.%20Between%202002%20and%202018%20he%20was%20Principal%20Scientific%20Adviser%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVtv5JOVOQW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVtv5JOVOQW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1875455884471759350%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%204%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20autobiography%2C%20India%20Rising%2C%20highlights%20his%20leadership%20in%20designing%20and%20executing%20the%20peaceful%20nuclear%20explosion%20experiment%20at%20Pokhran%20in%201974.%20It%20also%20documents%20his%20leadership%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20(DAE)%20team%20that%20designed%20the%20nuclear%20devices%20for%20the%201998%20Pokhran%20tests%20in%20cooperation%20with%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BDr%20Rajagopala%20Chidambaram%2C%20an%20eminent%20physicist%20and%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20distinguished%20scientists%2C%20passed%20away%20this%20morning%20(4%20January%202025)%20at%203%3A20%20am.%20Dr%20Chidambaram's%20unparalleled%20contributions%20to%20India's%20scientific%20and%20strategic%20capabilities%20and%20his%20visionary%20leadership%20in%20science%20and%20technology%20will%20forever%20be%20remembered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Chidambaram%20held%20numerous%20prestigious%20roles%20throughout%20his%20illustrious%20career%2C%20including%20Principal%20Scientific%20Adviser%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20(2001-2018)%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Bhabha%20Atomic%20Research%20Centre%20(1990-1993)%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%2C%20and%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20(1993-2000).%20He%20was%20also%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Governors%20of%20the%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%20(1994-1995)%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20IAEA's%20Commission%20of%20Eminent%20Persons%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20organisation's%20vision%20for%202020%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Chidambaram%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20India's%20nuclear%20capabilities.%20He%20was%20integral%20to%20the%20nation's%20first%20nuclear%20test%20in%201974%20and%20led%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20team%20during%20the%20Pokhran-II%20nuclear%20tests%20in%201998%2C%20firmly%20establishing%20India%20as%20a%20nuclear%20power%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20world-class%20physicist%2C%20Dr.%20Chidambaram's%20research%20in%20high-pressure%20physics%2C%20crystallography%2C%20and%20materials%20science%20significantly%20advanced%20the%20scientific%20community's%20understanding%20of%20these%20fields.%20His%20pioneering%20work%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20modern%20materials%20science%20research%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201936%2C%20Dr%20Chidambaram%20was%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Presidency%20College%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%2C%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Chidambaram%20was%20a%20visionary%20leader%20who%20believed%20in%20the%20power%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20to%20drive%20national%20development.%20He%20championed%20initiatives%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20energy%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20strategic%20self-reliance%2C%20and%20he%20steered%20numerous%20projects%20that%20significantly%20advanced%20India's%20science%20and%20technology%20landscape.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20initiating%20India's%20indigenous%20development%20of%20supercomputers%20and%20conceptualising%20the%20National%20Knowledge%20Network%2C%20which%20connected%20research%20and%20educational%20institutions%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ardent%20advocate%20of%20applying%20science%20and%20technology%20to%20national%20development%2C%20Dr%20Chidambaram%20established%20programmes%20such%20as%20the%20Rural%20Technology%20Action%20Groups%20and%20the%20Society%20for%20Electronic%20Transactions%20and%20Security.%20He%20also%20emphasised%20'Coherent%20Synergy'%20in%20India's%20scientific%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recognition%20of%20his%20exceptional%20contributions%2C%20Dr%20Chidambaram%20was%20honoured%20with%20prestigious%20accolades%2C%20including%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%201975%20and%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20in%201999.%20He%20received%20honorary%20doctorates%20from%20several%20universities%20and%20was%20a%20fellow%20of%20eminent%20Indian%20and%20international%20science%20academies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Chidambaram%20will%20be%20remembered%20as%20a%20trailblazer%2C%20an%20inspirational%20leader%2C%20and%20a%20dedicated%20mentor%20to%20countless%20scientists%20and%20engineers.%20His%20life's%20work%20propelled%20India%20to%20the%20forefront%20of%20global%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20and%20his%20legacy%20will%20continue%20to%20inspire%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735980900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fj2ot871g_r-chidambaram-_625x300_04_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fr-chidambaram-architect-of-operation-smiling-buddha-dies-at-88-7397081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20in%201936%2C%20Dr%20Chidambaram%20was%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Presidency%20College%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%2C%20Bengaluru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20next%20venture%20set%20to%20launch%20this%20year%3A%20a%20private%20preschool%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677403d7e5726ab18d0e2693%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20opening%20a%20new%20private%20preschool%20in%20Texas%20in%202025.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20funding%20a%20new%20private%20preschool%20in%20Texas%20called%20Ad%20Astra.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20set%20to%20open%20its%20doors%20th