0the%20school%20to%20open%20in%202025.%20Per%20the%20permit%2C%20the%20preschool%20can%20admit%20up%20to%2021%20students%20in%20its%20first%20year%20of%20operation.%20The%20school's%20application%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.bwbx.io%2Fdocuments%2Fusers%2FiqjWHBFdfxIU%2FrUU_RDpkhmuQ%2Fv0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematerials%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20obtained%20by%20Bloomberg%20said%20that%20the%20school's%20long-term%20goal%20is%20expanding%20into%20a%20university%20focused%20on%20STEM%20learning.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Musk's%20name%20does%20not%20appear%20in%20any%20of%20the%20school's%20application%20materials%20to%20the%20state%2C%20his%20foundation%20donated%20%24100%20million%20to%20get%20the%20preschool%20up%20and%20running%2C%20according%20to%20tax%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20social%20media%20website%20Twitter%20turned%20X%2C%20Musk%20is%20not%20primarily%20known%20for%20his%20influence%20on%20education.%20However%2C%20this%20isn't%20his%20first%20investment%20into%20the%20field%20%E2%80%94%20in%202014%2C%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fat-elon-musk-school-ad-astra-kids-can-make-flamethrowers-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopened%20a%20school%20also%20named%20Ad%20Astra%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20created%20for%20his%20kids%20and%20the%20kids%20of%20his%20SpaceX%20employees%2C%20which%20stopped%20its%20in-person%20operations%20after%20Musk's%20kids%20graduated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20billionaires%20to%20donate%20to%20schools%20and%20universities.%20Ad%20Astra's%20opening%2C%20however%2C%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20taking%20office%20for%20his%20second%20term.%20Musk%20is%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20Trump%2C%20tasked%20with%20leading%20a%20new%20cost-cutting%20commission%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-delete-cfpb-elon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-overdraft-fees-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Amid%20calls%20to%20eliminate%20the%20Education%20Department%20and%20give%20states%20more%20control%20over%20classrooms%2C%20Musk%20could%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20shaping%20education%20policy%20by%20offering%20advice%20to%20Trump%20and%20lawmakers.%20DOGE%20does%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20we%20need%20significant%20reform%20in%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FElonClipsX%2Fstatus%2F1856029700847505710%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20event%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20seems%20to%20regard%20as%20its%20primary%20duty%20foisting%20propaganda%20on%20our%20children%20as%20opposed%20to%20getting%20them%20a%20good%20education.%20It's%20insane%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20priority%20should%20be%20to%20teach%20kids%20skills%20that%20they%20will%20find%20useful%20later%20in%20life%20and%20leave%20any%20sort%20of%20social%20propaganda%20out%20of%20the%20classroom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAd%20Astra%20and%20Musk%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af933dcf-1421-4295-8332-f4c15aea0164%5C%22%3ENew%20priorities%20for%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAd%20Astra's%20website%20said%20it%20is%20not%20a%20Montessori%20school%2C%20but%20it%20operates%20like%20one%2C%20focusing%20on%20child-centered%20education%20and%20individualized%20lessons.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adastraschool.org%2Fapplynow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplication%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20school%20also%20encourages%20parental%20involvement%2C%20saying%20that%20Ad%20Astra%20wants%