22de1a17d3-5510-4fc4-9f7e-af7eb6893fd7%5C%22%3EI%20know%20that%20women%20are%20valued%20for%20looking%20young%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChristine%20Hall%2C%20an%20aesthetic%20doctor%20at%20London's%20Taktouk%20Clinic%2C%20told%20me%20that%20since%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20skincare%20has%20replaced%20makeup%20as%20the%20aesthetic%20focus%20for%20many%20women%20and%20girls.%20This%20reflects%20a%20shift%20from%20the%20heavily%20made-up%20look%20of%20the%20mid-2010s%20%E2%80%94%20with%20many%20celebrities%20revealing%20they've%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrities-who-talked-about-removing-implants-fillers-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiller%20removed%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20toward%20looking%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20and%20effortless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20by%20%26quot%3Bnatural%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20mean%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20worn%20a%20lot%20of%20makeup%20and%20am%20happy%20to%20go%20out%20and%20about%20bare-faced%2C%20so%20I%20was%20pleased%20that%20societal%20expectations%20changed.%20But%20the%20focus%20shifting%20from%20makeup%20to%20antiaging%20just%20as%20my%20first%20wrinkles%20appeared%20made%20me%20feel%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-follow-notox-trend-anti-aging-without-botox-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAntiaging%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20big%20business%20for%20centuries%2C%20as%20Western%20cultures%20traditionally%20value%20women%20for%20beauty%20and%20fertility%2C%20which%20are%20seen%20as%20synonymous%20with%20youth.%20These%20ideals%20followed%20women%20when%20they%20entered%20the%20workforce%20in%20greater%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20beautiful%20appearance%2C%20especially%20for%20women%2C%20can%20definitely%20lead%20to%20advantages%20on%20the%20relationship%20market%2C%20but%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20jobs%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20promotions%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20so%20many%20different%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Hermans%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20studying%20cosmetic%20procedures%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Social%20and%20Behavioral%20Sciences%20at%20Tilburg%20University%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPsychologists%20point%20to%20a%20phenomenon%20called%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhalo-effect-resumes-applicants-employers-wrong-choice-hiring-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalo%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20people%20unconsciously%20assume%20an%20attractive%20person%20has%20positive%20traits%2C%20such%20as%20trustworthiness%20and%20intelligence.%20A%202021%20study%20from%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Buffalo%20found%20that%20people%20perceived%20as%20attractive%20%26quot%3Bare%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20hired%2C%20receive%20better%20evaluations%2C%20and%20get%20paid%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20wanting%20to%20cling%20to%20our%20youth%20makes%20sense%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20shame%20anyone%20for%20having%20treatments%20like%20Botox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20Rachel%20Hosie%20in%20a%20pink%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676598071cee543535a881bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20like%20my%20skin%2C%20but%20I%20wonder%20if%20I%20should%20get%20Botox%20when%20I%20see%20women%20without%20lines%20on%20their%20faces.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20FDA%20approved%20Botox%20for%20cosmetic%20use%20in%202002%2C%20Gen%20X%20started%20the%20trend%20of%20facial%20%26quot%3Btweakments%26quot%3B%20in%20earnest.%20It%20was%20taken%20to%20new%20heights%20by%20millennials%20amid%20the%20rise%20of%20social%20media%20and%20filters%20that%20made%20them%20appear%20wrinkle-free.%20The%20Kardashian-esque%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A