C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%2016%20or%2017%2C%20it%20was%20all%20about%20blue%20eyeshadow%20and%20putting%20on%20as%20much%20foundation%20as%20possible.%20And%20now%20obviously%20the%20trend%20is%20kids%20wanting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsephora-kids-sleepaway-camps-ban-expensive-skincare-beauty-products-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrunk%20Elephant%3C%2Fa%3E%20products%20and%20acids%20on%20their%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christine%20Hall%20in%20scrubs%20sitting%20in%20a%20chair%20in%20front%20of%20a%20plant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad5e991c1cc343d47fb09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223939%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Christine%20Hall%20has%20seen%20aesthetic%20trends%20change%20over%20time.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blackett%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECommenting%20more%20widely%20on%20beauty%20trends%2C%20Hall%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BNobody%20wants%20to%20wear%20makeup.%20Everyone%20wants%20to%20have%20natural%2C%20glowing%20skin.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20aesthetic%20treatments%20are%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20acceptable%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20combination%20has%20in%20part%20ushered%20in%20what's%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40carriagesofharleystreet%2Fvideo%2F7421981757165161761%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundetectable%26quot%3B%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20beauty.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20faces%20of%20Lindsay%20Lohan%2C%2038%2C%20and%20Christina%20Aguilera%2C%2044%2C%20have%20been%20the%20subjects%20of%20online%20fascination%20because%20they%20suddenly%20looked%20dramatically%20younger%20without%20the%20tell-tale%20signs%20of%20cosmetic%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Lindsay%20Lohan%20in%202019%20and%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765a79b1cee543535a8879b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELindsay%20Lohan%20in%20October%202019%20(left)%20and%20November%202024.%3Cp%3ESantiago%20Felipe%2FGetty%20Images%2C%20James%20Devaney%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20average%20person%20who%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20resources%20as%20celebrities%2C%20this%20presents%20a%20paradox%20between%20wanting%20the%20result%20of%20treatments%20to%20look%20natural%20while%20also%20making%20enough%20of%20a%20difference%20to%20justify%20the%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20I%20tried%20what%20I%20had%20hoped%20would%20be%20the%20holy%20grail%20of%20antiaging%20treatments%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrotox-review-botox-antiaging-treatment-smoothes-wrinkles-lines-freezing-face-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrotox%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20hefty%20cost%20of%20%C2%A3495%20(%24657).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPopular%20in%20Korea%20but%20relatively%20new%20in%20the%20West%2C%20diluted%20Botox%20is%20injected%20into%20the%20skin's%20surface%20rather%20than%20muscles%2C%20preventing%20a%20frozen-looking%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hoped%20my%20skin%20would%20be%20wrinkle-free%20while%20maintaining%20all%20movement%20and%20expression.%20While%20my%20skin%20glowed%2C%20the%20effect%20on%20my%20fine%20lines%20was%20negligible%20and%20wore%20off%20over%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Rachel%20Hosie's%20face%20before%20and%20after%20microtox.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad8a252dd0818d1a69316%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20face%20before%20microtox%20(left)%20and%20two%20weeks%20after.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20I%20look%20at%20photos%20of%20myself%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20my%20wedding%20and%20wince%20at%20my%20forehead%20lines%2C%20I%20think%2C%20sure%2C%20Botox%20may%20be%20contributing%20to%20low%20self-esteem%20among%20women%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20change%20the%20world%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20everyone%20else%20is%20giving%20in%20and%20walking%20around%20with%20shiny%2C%20smooth%20foreheads%2C%20maybe%20I%20should%2C%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246f6147c-2fc3-486f-9c0b-aa8d523dd179%5C%22%3EI%20want%20to%20look%20like%20myself%20at%20my%20wedding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20now%20less%20than%20six%20months%20until%20my%20wedding%2C%20and%20considering%20most%20people%20get%20Botox%20every%20three%20to%20six%20months%2C%20I've%20nearly%20run%20out%20of%20time%20to%20do%20a%20trial%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHermans%20told%20me%20that%20a%20big%20predictor%20of%20whether%20someone%20will%20get%20any%20kind%20of%20aesthetic%20treatment%20is%20whether%20those%20in%20their%20social%20circle%20have%20done%20so.%20None%20of%20my%20close%20friends%20have%20had%20Botox%20%E2%80%94%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20I've%20decided%20not%20to%20get%20Botox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20may%20have%20crinkles%20and%20lines%20on%20my%20face%2C%20I%20also%20know%20who%20I%20am%2C%20which%20I%20was%20still%20working%20out%20a%20decade%20ago.%20My%20face%20looks%20like%20me%2C%20lines%20included.%20Just%20as%20my%20muscle%20definition%20reflects%20my%20love%20of%20strength%20training%2C%20my%20forehead%20lines%20reflect%20that%20I've%20embraced%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20have%20moments%20where%20I%20catch%20my%20reflection%20in%20harsh%20lighting%20or%20an%20action%20shot%20photo%20and%20don't%20like%20what%20I%20see.%20But%20perhaps%20reframing%20how%20I%20think%20about%20my%20looks%20is%20the%20answer%2C%20not%20Botox.%20After%20all%2C