matthew-livelsberger-had-no-animosity-towards-trump-suffered-from-ptsd-fbi%2Farticleshow%2F116933571.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116933571.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20FBI%20reported%20that%20Matthew%20Livelsberger%2C%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20that%20exploded%20outside%20the%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20had%20no%20ill%20will%20towards%20President-elect%20Trump.%20Livelsberger%2C%20an%20Army%20soldier%20from%20Colorado%20Springs%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20suffered%20from%20PTSD%20and%20personal%20issues.%20Officials%20confirmed%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%2C%20involving%20a%20gunshot%20wound.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftesla-cybertruck-driver-matthew-livelsberger-had-no-animosity-towards-trump-suffered-from-ptsd-fbi%2Farticleshow%2F116933571.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftesla-cybertruck-driver-matthew-livelsberger-had-no-animosity-towards-trump-suffered-from-ptsd-fbi%2Famp_articleshow%2F116933571.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftesla-cybertruck-driver-matthew-livelsberger-had-no-animosity-towards-trump-suffered-from-ptsd-fbi%2Famp_articleshow%2F116933571.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Six%20Indian-Americans%20Sworn-In%20As%20Members%20Of%20US%20House%20Of%20Representatives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20momentous%20occasion%20for%20Indian%20Americans%2C%20six%20of%20their%20leaders%20on%20Friday%20were%20sworn-in%20as%20the%20members%20of%20the%20US%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20the%20largest%20so%20far%20for%20this%20minority%20ethnic%20community%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20first%20sworn%20in%20twelve%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20the%20sole%20Indian%20American%20Member%20of%20Congress%20and%20only%20the%20third%20in%20US%20history.%20Now%2C%20our%20coalition%20is%20six%20strong!%20I%20am%20excited%20to%20welcome%20even%20more%20Indian%20Americans%20to%20the%20halls%20of%20Congress%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come!%26quot%3B%20Congressman%20Dr%20Ami%20Bera%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBera%2C%20the%20senior%20most%20of%20them%2C%20who%20has%20been%20sworn-in%20for%20the%20seventh%20consecutive%20term%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20seventh%20Congressional%20District%20of%20California%2C%20also%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20all%20the%20six%20Indian%20American%20Congressman%20from%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhash%20Subramanian%2C%20who%20represents%20the%2010th%20Congressional%20District%20of%20Virginia%20is%20the%20newest%20Indian%20American%20to%20be%20a%20member%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%20%26quot%3BFirst%20day%20of%20work!%20Honoured%20to%20be%20sworn%20into%20the%20%23119th%20Congress%2C%20and%20excited%20to%20get%20to%20work%20to%20deliver%20results%20for%20VA10%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20he%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20him%20along%20with%20his%20family%20and%20House%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReady%20to%20Serve%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congressman%20Shri%20Thanedar%20who%20represents%20the%2013th%20Congressional%20District%20of%20Michigan%20as%20he%20posted%20a%20selfie%20of%20his%20from%20the%20House%20floor.%20All%20the%20six%20Indian%20American%20lawmakers%20are%20from%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20voted%20for%20House%20Minority%20Leader%20Hakeem%20Jeffries%20in%20the%20election%20for%20House%20Speakership.%20Republican%20Mike%20Johnson%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20House%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongressman%20Ro%20Khanna%20represents%20the%2017th%20Congressional%20District%20of%20California%20and%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%20represents%20the%20eighth%20Congressional%20District%20of%20Illinois.%20Congresswoman%20Pramila%20Jayapal%2C%20representing%20the%20seventh%20Congressional%20District%20of%20Washington%20state%2C%20is%20the%20first%20ever%20Indian%20American%20woman%20to%20be%20elected%20to%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20three%20-%20Khanna%2C%20Krishnamoorthi%20and%20Jayapal%20-%20have%20been%20sworn-in%20for%20a%20fifth%20consecutive%20term%2C%20during%20which%20they%20have%20emerged%20as%20powerful%20lawmakers%20in%20their%20own%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnamoorthi%20is%20a%20Ranking%20Member%20of%20the%20powerful%20China%20Committee%20and%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20House%20Intelligence%20Committee.%20Jayapal%20is%20leader%20of%20the%20highly%20powerful%20progressive%20group%20of%20lawmakers.%20Khanna%20is%20not%20only%20a%20member%20of%20several%20powerful%20House%20committees%2C%20but%20also%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20presidential%20candidate%20in%20the%20years%20to%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20six%20Indian%20Americans%20constitute%20an%20informal%20Samosa%20Caucus%2C%20a%20term%20coined%20by%20Krishnamoorthi.%20When%20sworn%20in%20for%20the%20first%20term%20in%202012%2C%20Dr%20Bera%20had%20then%20wished%20to%20have%2010%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Indian%20Americans%20aspiring%20to%20be%20elected%20to%20the%20House%20lost%20elections%20either%20during%20the%20primaries%20or%20in%20the%20November%205%20general%20elections.%20At%20least%20three%20of%20them%20were%20women%3A%20Sushila%20Jaipal%2C%20Bhavani%20Patel%20and%20Krystal%20Kaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalip%20Singh%20Saund%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20American%20to%20be%20elected%20to%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20in%201957.%20Also%2C%20the%20first%20Sikh%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20for%20three%20consecutive%20ter