ding%20on%20to%20a%20stable%20job%2C%20descended%20into%20the%20world%20of%20cybercrime%2C%20largely%20motivated%20by%20greed%20and%20lust%20for%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModus%20Operandi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20virtual%20international%20mobile%20number%20procured%20through%20an%20app%2C%20Tushar%20created%20fake%20profiles%20on%20popular%20dating%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20such%20as%20Bumble%20and%20Snapchat.%20He%20posed%20as%20a%20US-based%20freelance%20model%20visiting%20India%2C%20using%20a%20fabricated%20persona%20with%20photos%20and%20stories%20stolen%20from%20an%20actual%20Brazilian%20model.%20His%20targets%20were%20primarily%20women%20aged%2018-30%2C%20whom%20he%20befriended%20through%20these%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20gained%20their%20trust%2C%20Tushar%20would%20request%20their%20phone%20numbers%20and%20intimate%20photos%20or%20videos%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20friendship.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20his%20victims%2C%20he%20saved%20the%20visuals%20on%20his%20phone.%20Initially%2C%20these%20activities%20were%20conducted%20for%20personal%20amusement%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20they%20evolved%20into%20a%20systematic%20scheme%20of%20extortion%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Tushar%20used%20these%20visuals%20to%20blackmail%20women%20into%20giving%20him%20money.%20If%20a%20victim%20refused%20his%20demands%20for%20money%2C%20he%20would%20threaten%20to%20upload%20their%20explicit%20content%20online%20or%20sell%20it%20on%20the%20dark%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Victims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20findings%2C%20Tushar%20engaged%20with%20more%20than%20500%20women%20on%20Bumble%20and%20over%20200%20on%20Snapchat%20and%20WhatsApp.%20He%20accumulated%20a%20trove%20of%20intimate%20content%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20blackmail%20his%20victims.%20One%20such%20case%20came%20to%20light%20when%20a%20second-year%20Delhi%20University%20student%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Cyber%20Police%20Station%20on%20December%2013%2C%202024.%20Her%20ordeal%20began%20in%20January%20of%20the%20same%20year%20when%20she%20connected%20with%20Tushar%20on%20Bumble.%20He%20introduced%20himself%20as%20a%20US-based%20model%20and%20initiated%20a%20friendship%20that%20later%20transitioned%20to%20private%20chats%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20Snapchat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20exchanges%2C%20the%20victim%20shared%20personal%20photos%20and%20videos%20with%20him.%20When%20she%20requested%20to%20meet%20in%20person%2C%20he%20consistently%20avoided%20her%20under%20various%20pretexts.%20Soon%20after%2C%20he%20sent%20her%20one%20of%20her%20private%20videos%20and%20demanded%20money%2C%20threatening%20to%20leak%20or%20sell%20the%20material%20if%20she%20did%20not%20comply.%20Initially%2C%20the%20student%20succumbed%20to%20the%20pressure%2C%20paying%20a%20small%20amount%20while%20explaining%20her%20financial%20constraints%20as%20a%20student.%20However%2C%20Tushar's%20incessant%20demands%20pushed%20her%20to%20confide%20in%20her%20family%20and%20lodge%20a%20formal%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cyber%20Police%20Station%20of%20West%20Delhi%20formed%20a%20team%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20ACP%20Arvind%20Yadav.%20A%20combination%20of%20technical%20analysis%20and%20intelligence%20gathering%20helped%20the%20team%20trace%20Tushar's%20activities%20and%20identify%20him%20as%20the%20accused.%20A%20swift%20raid%20in%20Shakarpur%20led%20to%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20operation%2C%20the%20police%20recovered%20a%20mobile%20phone%20containing%20incriminating%20data%2C%20a%20virtual%20international%20mobile%20number%20linked%20to%20his%20criminal%20activities%2C%20and%2013%20credit%20cards%20from%20various%20banks.%20The%20police%20also%20retrieved%20over%2060%20WhatsApp%20chat%20records%20with%20women%20from%2