the%20man%20behind%20the%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20bombing%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%20Matthew%20Livelsberger%20described%20the%20attack%20as%20a%20personal%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccleansing%20his%20mind%E2%80%9D%20and%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfeckless%20leadership%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20nation%20he%20believed%20was%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20collapse.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLivelsberger%20left%20two%20digital%20notes%20on%20a%20charred%20mobile%20phone%20found%20in%20the%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20he%20rented%20before%20detonating%20it%20outside%20the%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20on%20January%201.%20The%20notes%20shed%20light%20on%20his%20motive%20for%20the%20bombing%20and%20later%20taking%20his%20life%20by%20gunshot.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20not%20a%20terrorist%20attack%2C%20it%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20Livelsberger%20wrote%20in%20a%20notes%20app%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F01%2F03%2Fus-news%2Fmatthew-livelsberger-claimed-las-vegas-cybertruck-bombing-wasnt-a-terror-attack-in-note%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20I%20personally%20do%20it%20now%3F%20I%20needed%20to%20cleanse%20my%20mind%20of%20the%20brothers%20I've%20lost%20and%20relieve%20myself%20of%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20lives%20I%20took.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20blast%20injured%20seven%20people.%20Livelsberger's%20body%20was%20burned%20beyond%20recognition%20and%20was%20later%20identified%20through%20his%20passport%20and%20military%20ID%20found%20in%20the%20vehicle.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20veteran%20of%20Afghanistan%20tours%20in%202017%20and%202018%2C%20Livelsberger%20was%20known%20for%20his%20patriotism%20and%20support%20of%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump.%20Federal%20officials%20suggested%20that%20his%20actions%20may%20have%20been%20driven%20by%20severe%20post-traumatic%20stress%2