ble%20recommendation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Trump%20will%20not%20face%20imprisonment%2C%20the%20sentencing%20will%20see%20the%2078-year-old%20Republican%20entering%20the%20White%20House%20as%20a%20convicted%20felon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20hush%20money%20case%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hush%20money%20case%20stems%20from%20an%20alleged%20payment%20made%20by%20Mr%20Trump's%20former%20lawyer%2C%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20to%20adult%20film%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels%20-%20who%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20paid%20the%20money%20to%20stay%20quiet%20about%20her%20alleged%20affair%20with%20the%20former%20President%20during%20the%202016%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%2C%20agreed%20to%20pay%20Ms%20Daniels%20%24130%2C000%20in%20exchange%20for%20her%20silence.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20did%20so%20at%20Mr%20Trump's%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20he%20was%20convicted%20of%2034%20felony%20counts%20for%20falsifying%20business%20records%20connected%20to%20the%20payment%20-%20a%20violation%20of%20state%20election%20law.%20While%20hush%20money%20payments%20are%20not%20illegal%2C%20the%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney's%20Office%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20a%20crime%26quot%3B%20by%20improperly%20recording%20the%20money%20with%20which%20he%20reimbursed%20Cohen%20as%20legal%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20attorney%20had%20sought%20to%20have%20the%20case%20dismissed%20on%20multiple%20grounds%20since%20then%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20landmark%20ruling%20last%20year%20that%20former%20US%20presidents%20have%20sweeping%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%20for%20a%20range%20of%20official%20acts%20committed%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20denounces%20his%20sentencing%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President-elect%2C%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20lodge%20an%20appeal%20that%20could%20potentially%20delay%20his%20sentencing%2C%20denounced%20the%20decision%2C%20calling%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Billegitimate%20political%20attack%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20illegitimate%20political%20attack%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20Rigged%20Charade%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Republican's%20spokesperson%2C%20Mr%20Trump's%20sentencing%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bviolation%20of%20presidential%20immunity%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BToday's%20order%20by%20the%20deeply%20conflicted%2C%20Acting%20Justice%20Merchan%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20DA%20Witch%20Hunt%20is%20a%20direct%20violation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Immunity%20decision%20and%20other%20longstanding%20jurisprudence%2C%26quot%3B%20Steven%20Cheung%2C%20Trump's%20incoming%20communications%20director%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735963200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnlie56s8_donald-trump_625x300_23_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-hush-money-case-in-which-donald-trump-will-be-sentenced-before-taking-office-7396246%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20will%20be%20sentenced%20in%20the%20hush%20money%20case%20on%20January%2010%2C%20days%20before%20his%20planned%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-hush-money-case-in-which-donald-trump-will-be-sentenced-before-taking-office-7396246%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Calls%20HMPV%20Outbreak%20'Winter%20Occurrence'%2C%20India%20Says%20'Don't%20Panic'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPhotos%20and%20videos%20of%20people%20wearing%20masks%20in%20hospitals%20in%20China%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20local%20reports%20said%20the%20outbreak%20of%20HMPV%2C%20which%20was%20discovered%20in%202001%2C%20scenes%20similar%20to%20the%20Covid%20outbreak%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20later%20turned%20into%20a%20global%20pandemic%20and%20led%20to%20over%207%20million%20deaths%20globally.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-china-gets-another-covid-like-scare-beijing-calls-it-winter-occurance-7394374%5C%22%3EBeijing%20issued%20a%20press%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20address%20such%20concerns.%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20%26quot%3BRespiratory%20infections%20tend%20to%20peak%20during%20the%20winter%20season%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReassuring%20citizens%20and%20tourists%2C%20she%20said%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20the%20Chinese%20government%20cares%20about%20the%20health%20of%20Chinese%20citizens%20and%20foreigners%20coming%20to%20China%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20safe%20to%20travel%20in%20China%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20affected%20by%20COVID-19.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-cause-for-alarm-indian-health-agency-on-hmpv-virus-spreading-in-china-7392255%5C%22%3EDirectorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20(DGHS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20official%20Dr%20Atul%20Goel%20has%20asked%20people%20not%20to%20panic%20over%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20in%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20news%20doing%20the%20rounds%20about%20a%20Metapneumovirus%20outbreak%20in%20China.%20Let%20me%20be%20very%20clear%20on%20that%20count.%20Metapneumovirus%20is%20like%20any%20other%20respiratory%20virus%20which%20causes%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20and%20in%20the%20very%20old%20and%20the%20very%20young%20it%20could%20cause%20flu-like%20symptoms%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Goel%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20analysed%20data%20on%20the%20respiratory%20outbreaks%20within%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20substantial%20increase%20in%20December%202024%20data%20and%20no%20cases%20which%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20large%20numbers%20from%20any%20of%20our%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20is%20yet%20to%20issue%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20virus%20in%20China%20and%20no%20state%20of%20emergency%20has%20been%20declared%20by%20the%20global%20health%20body%20or%20Beijing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECountries%20neighbouring%20China%20are%20strictly%20monitoring%20the%20situation.%20Hong%20Kong%20has%20reported%20a%20few%20cases%20of%20HMPV.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhmpv-outbreak-in-china-symptoms-spread-and-what-you-should-know-7389007%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20HMPV%20is%20a%20respiratory%20virus%20that%20causes%20upper%20and%20lower%20respiratory%20infections.%20It%20affects%20individuals%20across%20all%20age%20groups%2C%20with%20young%20children%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20those%20with%20compromised%20immune%20systems%20being%20most%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20symptoms%20of%20HMPV%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20flu%20and%20other%20respiratory%20infections.%20Common%20signs%20include%20cough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%20In%20severe%20cases%2C%20the%20virus%20can%20lead%20to%20complications%20like%20bronchitis%20or%20pneumonia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735963020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Foun77ts8_china-covid_625x300_09_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co