plosives%20experts%20said%20the%20level%20of%20damage%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20blast%20was%20likely%20limited%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20materials%20used%20and%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20apparent%20attack.%3Cp%3EWADE%20VANDERVORT%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20told%20BI%20the%20explosives%20detonated%20in%20an%20apparent%20attack%20outside%20a%20Trump%20hotel%20didn't%20appear%20sophisticated.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20explosives%20expert%20said%20the%20incident%2C%20where%20the%20driver%20was%20an%20active-duty%20Army%20service%20member%2C%20appeared%20%26quot%3Bpoorly%20executed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAuthorities%20said%20the%20explosives%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20what%20we%20would%20expect%20from%20an%20individual%20with%20this%20type%20of%20military%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EExplosive%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20damage%20from%20the%20materials%20detonated%20inside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-fire-outside-trump-hotel-one-dead-others-injured-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20Cybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20would%20likely%20have%20been%20worse%20if%20the%20items%20used%20had%20been%20more%20sophisticated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20explosive-laden%20Cybertruck%2C%20which%20authorities%20say%20carried%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FLVMPD%2Fstatus%2F1874622641983943037%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egasoline%20tanks%2C%20camping%20fuel%2C%20and%20large%20firework%20mortars%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20injured%20at%20least%20seven%20people.%20The%20driver%2C%20an%20active-duty%20Army%20service%20member%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybertruck-explosion-driver-matthew-alan-livelsberger-army-soldier-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Alan%20Livelsberger%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20shot%20himself%20moments%20before%20the%20explosives%20detonated%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20took%20to%20social%20media%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20praise%20the%20Cybertruck's%20design%20and%20suggest%20it%20helped%20limit%20the%20damage%20of%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Glumac%2C%20a%20mechanical%20science%20and%20engineering%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign%2C%20told%20BI%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20volume%20of%20the%20explosion%20was%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20types%20of%20explosives%20used.%20Glumac%20said%20this%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpoorly%20executed%26quot%3B%20incident%20if%20the%20intent%20was%20to%20cause%20major%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20the%20types%20of%20fuels%20here%20to%20make%20into%20a%20large%20scale%20destruction%20kind%20of%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20Glumac%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlumac%20said%20similar%20improvised%20explosive%20device%20blasts%20look%20very%20different%20from%20what%20occurred%20on%20January%201.%20He%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20Oklahoma%20City%20Bombing%20in%201995%2C%20when%20Army%20veteran%20Timothy%20McVeigh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Fhistory%2Ffamous-cases%2Foklahoma-city-bombing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetonated%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20explosive-laden%20rental%20truck%20that%20killed%20168%20people%20and%20reduced%20a%20third%20of%20the%20federal%20building%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20very%20carefully%20planned.%20They%20knew%20what%20they%20were%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Glumac%20said%20about%20the%20Oklahoma%20City%20Bombing%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Cybertruck%20explosion%20on%20January%201%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20appeared%20%26quot%3Bvery%20improvised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22608e9b17-c533-42d9-a6da-d2bd4ed1d8c1%5C%22%3E'The%20level%20of%20sophistication%20is%20not%20what%20we%20would%20expect%20from%20an%20individual%20with%20this%20type%20of%20military%20experience'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECar%20and%20truck%20bombs%20were%20a%20key%20feature%20of%20the%20wars%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20which%20the%20suspect%20deployed%20at%20least%20three%20times.%20In%20many%20of%20those%20instances%2C%20vehicles%20were%20packed%20with%20enough%20explosives%20to%20blast%20fortified%20positions%20or%20take%20down%20buildings.%20The%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20similarly%20suggested%20that%20heavily%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-tank-explosion-so-massive-likely-russia-rolling-bomb-ukraine-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etanks%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20used%20as%20rolling%20car%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20spoke%20about%20the%20explosive%20materials%20used%20in%20the%20incident%20during%20a%20Thursday%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20level%20of%20sophistication%20is%20not%20what%20we%20would%20expect%20from%20an%20individual%20with%20this%20type%20of%20military%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKenny%20Cooper%2C%20an%20assistant%20special%20agent%20in%20charge%20for%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Alcohol%2C%20Tobacco%2C%20Firearms%20and%20Explosives%2C%20said%20at%20a%20Las%20Vegas%20Metropolitan%20Police%20press%20conference%2C%20adding%20that%20most%20of%20the%20materials%20in%20the%20vehicle%20were%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20fuel%20a%20greater%20explosion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20Rangwala%2C%20a%20fire%20protection%20engineering%20professor%20at%20Worcester%20Polytechnic%20Institute%2C%20said%20that%20the%20driver%20may%20have%20miscalculated%20the%20explosion%2C%20and%20it%20might%20not%20have%20been%20released%20instantaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20explosives%20might%20not%20have%20triggered%20on%20time%20systematically%2C%26quot%3B%20Rangwala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20to%20create%20an%20instantaneous%20energy%20release%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20bomb%2C%20is%20for%20all%20of%20the%20energetic%20material%20to%20ignite%20in%20micro-%20or%20milli-seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20Jim%20Wesevich%2C%20a%20global%20service%20line%20leader%20of%20forensics%20at%20safety%20and%20security%20firm%20Jensen%20Hughes%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20written%20commentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20military%20official%20told%20BI%20that%20Livelsberger%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20a%20bomb%20maker.%26quot%3B%20But%20his%20military%20occupational%20specialty%20(MOS)%20within%20the%2010th%20Special%20Forces%20Group%20was%2018Z%2C%20making%20him%20a%20special%20forces%20operations%20sergeant%2C%20which%20the%20Army%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Btrains%20and%20maintains%20proficiency%20in%20all%20major%20duties%20associated%20with%20Special%20Forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooper%20said%20it%20was%20too%20early%20to%20know%20if%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bsophisticated%20connectivity%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20components%20or%20to%20%26quot%3Bgive%20any%20determination%26quot%3B%20as%20to%20how%20the%20explosion%20was%20initiated.%20Officials%20said%20they%20discovered%20consumer%20fireworks%2C%20mortars%2C%20aerial%20shells%2C%20fuel%20enhancers%2C%20and%20explosive%20targets%20that%20Cooper%20said%20could%20be%20purchased%20at%20%26quot%3Bany%20sporting%20goods%20store.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a367daf-aa56-4916-af29-79bbc6f34f09%5C%22%3EExperts%20say%20a%20vehicle's%20design%20may%20shape%20the%20trajectory%20of%20a%20blast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1874566977005732014%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Cybertruck%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20possible%20choice%20for%20a%20car%20bomb%2C%20as%20its%20stainless%20steel%20armor%20will%20contain%20the%20blast%20better%20than%20any%20other%20commercial%20vehicle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20McMahill%2C%20sheriff%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Metropolitan%20Police%20Department%2C%20said%20the%20Cybertruck's%20design%20helped%20limit%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20this%20was%20a%20Cybertruck%20really%20limited%20the%20damage%20that%20occurred%20inside%20of%20the%20valet%20because%20it%20had%20most%20of%20the%20blast%20go%20up%20and%20through%20the%20truck%20and%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20McMahill%20said%20in%20a%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERangwala%20said%20the%20damage%20may%20have%20been%20partly%20limited%20because%20a%20Cybertruck's%20roof%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20large%20glass%20pane%2C%20would%20clear%20pressure%20from%20inside%20the%20vehicle%20early%20in%20the%20explosion.%20The%20pressure%20from%20an%20explosion%20would%20be%20felt%20on%20all%20sides%20equally%20if%20it%20wasn't%20relieved%20by%20going%20upward%20through%20the%20roof%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlumac%20and%20Brian%20Meacham%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20director%20of%20risk%20and%20regulatory%20consulting%20at%20Crux%20Consulting%20LLC%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20over%20email%2C%20said%20that%20they%20would%20have%20expected%20similar%20scenarios%20if%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20a%20traditional%20pickup%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Villahermosa%2C%20a%20US%20Army%20commander%20with%20a%20background%20in%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%2C%20said%20on%20X%20that%20photos%20of%20the%20items%20used%20in%20the%20blast%20suggest%20the%20explosives%20were%20%26quot%3Bpoorly%20constructed%20and%20poorly%20thought%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FEODHappyCaptain%2Fstatus%2F1874645629495910533%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20using%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20bombing%20to%20show%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%26quot%3B%20when%2C%20in%20his%20view%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20shows%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20explosive%20device%20that%20was%20used.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EStaff%20writer%20Ryan%20Pickrell%20contributed%20to%20this%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-las-vegas-trump-hotel-explosive-experts-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735956722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6776992e9de00e389eb41845%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-las-vegas-trump-hotel-explosive-experts-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Explosives%20experts%20told%20BI%20the%20design%20of%20the%20explosives%20that%20detonated%20outside%20the%20Trump%20Hotel%20didn't%20appear%20sophisticated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek%2CHasan%20Chowdhury)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-las-vegas-trump-hotel-explosive-experts-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bringing%20a%20tyrannical%20Ethiopian%20queen%20and%20her%20twins%20to%20life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735956557000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2634%2Flive%2F07891a80-bc86-11ef-a2ca-e99d0c9a24e3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0lg6151p32o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20compelling%20new%20audio%20drama%20shines%20a%20spotlight%20on%20Ethiopia's%20ancient%20Aksumite%20Empire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0lg6151p32o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0lg6151p32o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22ht