e%20industry's%20biggest%20names%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20opportunity%20for%20some%20newer%20entrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrinking%20is%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20preventable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcancer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr.%20Vivek%20Murthy%20said%20in%20the%20advisory%2C%20which%20also%20recommended%20placing%20a%20notice%20about%20the%20cancer%20risk%20on%20beer%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20spirits%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20how%20packs%20of%20cigarettes%20include%20warnings%20about%20their%20health%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20own%2C%20the%20recommendation%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20labels%20on%20booze%20will%20change.%20That%20would%20require%20an%20act%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurthy%20is%20also%20part%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20and%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20nominee%20for%20surgeon%20general%20after%20he%20takes%20office%20on%20January%2020.%20That%20nominee%2C%20Janette%20Nesheiwat%2C%20could%20take%20a%20different%20view%20on%20the%20advisory%20if%20she's%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20advisory%20prompted%20a%20response%20from%20some%20companies%20and%20the%20markets%20today.%20Here's%20what%20it%20might%20mean%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221325dc76-f3db-414e-b8d2-4d7e96a8a3fb%5C%22%3EShares%20of%20alcohol%20companies%20like%20Diageo%20and%20AB%20InBev%20lost%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20of%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20alcohol%20companies%20in%20the%20world%20were%20down%20Friday%20after%20the%20surgeon%20general%20released%20his%20advisory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Budweiser-maker%20Anheuser-Busch%20InBev%20closed%20down%202.8%25%20in%20Belgium.%20In%20London%2C%20shares%20of%20Diageo%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Captain%20Morgan%20rum%20and%20Ketel%20One%20vodka%2C%20closed%20nearly%204%25%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there's%20reason%20to%20doubt%20that%20the%20surgeon%20general's%20advisory%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20lot%20less%20drinking%20and%20fewer%20sales%20for%20the%20big%20booze%20makers%2C%20Kate%20Bernot%2C%20lead%20analyst%20at%20Sightlines%2C%20which%20researches%20the%20alcohol%20space%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnnual%20per-capita%20alcohol%20consumption%20in%20the%20US%20has%20hovered%20around%202%20%C2%BD%20gallons%20since%202012%2C%20Bernot%20said%2C%20citing%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Beer%20Wholesalers%20Association.%20Gallup%20polling%20shows%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20Americans%20who%20say%20that%20they%20drink%20alcohol%20has%20mostly%20stayed%20between%2060%25%20and%2065%25%20since%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20stability%20in%20habits%20comes%20despite%20previous%20research%20into%20the%20link%20between%20alcohol%20consumption%20and%20cancer%20as%20well%20as%20the%20growth%20of%20%26quot%3BDry%20January%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20commitment%20drinkers%20make%20to%20avoid%20drinking%20during%20this%20time%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20some%20people%20change%20their%20behavior%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20population-level%20dramatic%20shifts%20in%20alcohol%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256e09822-90fc-400f-84f4-515b79e10f03%5C%22%3EMakers%20of%20non-alcoholic%20beer%20and%20spirits%20could%20get%20a%20boost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20there%20is%20a%20nationwide%20shift%20away%20from%20alcohol%2C%20many%20of%20the%20big%20producers%20already%20have%20alcohol-free%20options%20that%20they%20have%20been%20ramping%20up%20for%20years.%20In%202023%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Constellation%20released%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbrands.com%2Fblogs%2Fnews%2Fwelcome-to-la-familia-corona%25C2%25AE-non-alcoholic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20non-alcoholic%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Corona%20beer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20diversification%20has%20been%20happening%20as%20a%20result%20of%20consumers'%20potential%20thoughts%20about%20alcohol's%20effect%20on%20their%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurthy's%20advisory%20came%20right%20as%20many%20drinkers%20are%20trying%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20their%20alcohol%20consumption%20in%20the%20new%20year%20or%20embarking%20on%20a%20Dry%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20potential%20win%20for%20many%20other%20brands%20that%20make%20alcohol-free%20beer%2C%20wine%2C%20gin%2C%20and%20other%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CMO%20of%20non-alcoholic%20spirit%20brand%20Spiritless%2C%20Tom%20Santangelo%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20sees%20these%20comments%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfront%20end%20of%20a%20tipping%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20guess%20is%20that%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20America%2C%20this%20surgeon%20general%20statement%20is%20kind%20of%20the%20message%20they%20need%20to%20come%20to%20a%20realization%20that%20this%20is%20something%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20Santangelo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20industry%20has%20already%20grown%20significantly%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20as%20alcohol%20moderation%20and%20abstention%20have%20become%20increasingly%20normalized.%20Similar%20to%20cigarettes%2C%20change%20may%20not%20come%20quickly%2C%20but%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20message%20that's%20going%20to%20carry%20a%20lot%20of%20weight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilan%20Martin%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20non-alcoholic%20spirit%20brand%20The%20Free%20Spirits%20Company%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20US%20Surgeon%20General's%20comments%20are%20another%20%26quot%3Bnugget%26quot%3B%20of%20insight%20that%20will%20contribute%20to%20cultural%20change%20around%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20teeny%20little%20nuggets%20sit%20in%20our%20minds%20and%20sit%20there%20at%20the%20point%20where%20we're%20ready%20to%20order%20our%20third%20drink%20and%20impact%20our%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20conversations%20among%20peers%20and%20in%20the%20media%20around%20drinking%20are%20contributing%20to%20changes%20in%20drinking%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAthletic%20Brewing%2C%20which%20sells%20non-alcoholic%20beer%2C%20similarly%20said%20that%20while%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20the%20ongoing%20discussions%20about%20alcohol%20and%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20%26quot%3Bhas%20never%20been%20anti-alcohol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20believe%20the%20alcohol%20and%20non-alcoholic%20sectors%20are%20synergistic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c66ab4d-fa7c-44dc-9898-fc7d1afac8e4%5C%22%3EInnovative%20soft%20drinks%2C%20from%20seltzer%20to%20kava%2C%20could%20benefit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20alcohol-free%20beer%20and%20cocktails%20with%20all%20the%20ingredients%20other%20than%20the%2C%20well%2C%20alcohol%2C%20there%20are%20other%20beverages%20that%20have%20attracted%20attention%20from%20the%20sober-curious%20%E2%80%94%20and%20could%20benefit%20if%20people%20cut%20back%20on%20booze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrities-getting-into-soda-business-with-healthy-drinks-social-media-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECelebrity%20seltzer%20and%20soda%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20pitch%20themselves%20as%20upscale%2C%20healthier%20soft%20drinks%2C%20BI%20reported%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkava-beverages-mitra-9-leilo-taste-test-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekava%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20beverage%20that's%20common%20to%20the%20Pacific%20and%20is%20supposed%20to%20help%20you%20relax%20and%20put%20you%20in%20a%20better%20mood.%20While%20the%20most%20authentic%20kava%20is%20served%20on%20its%20own%2C%20brands%20that%20have%20added%20juice%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20coloring%20before%20canni